WEBVTT

00:06.374 --> 00:08.576
male announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:08.609 --> 00:10.111
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES

00:10.144 --> 00:12.280
ARE CONSIDERED
ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:12.313 --> 00:13.614
IN NEW YORK CITY,

00:13.647 --> 00:14.815
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:14.848 --> 00:16.384
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:16.417 --> 00:18.119
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:18.152 --> 00:20.254
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:20.288 --> 00:22.056
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:24.358 --> 00:27.161
- BLESS YOU.
THE LORD SAID,

00:27.195 --> 00:29.497
WHAT GOES INTO
A MAN'S MOUTH

00:29.530 --> 00:31.665
CANNOT MAKE HIM UNCLEAN.

00:31.699 --> 00:34.402
FOR IT MOVES THROUGH
HIS STOMACH AND OUT HIS BODY.

00:34.435 --> 00:38.472
WHAT COMES OUT
OF A MAN'S MOUTH IS UNCLEAN,

00:38.506 --> 00:40.308
FOR IT COMES
FROM THE HEART,

00:40.341 --> 00:42.843
WHERE EVIL LURKS.

00:42.876 --> 00:46.247
IMMORALITY, ADULTERY, LUST!

00:46.280 --> 00:49.083
- HEY! WHY DON'T YOU
TAKE THAT ACT SOMEWHERE ELSE,

00:49.117 --> 00:51.352
PREACHER MAN?

00:51.385 --> 00:54.122
- AH, UH, DEFINITELY
GOT A SOUL BACK HERE

00:54.155 --> 00:55.556
WHO NEEDS SAVING.

00:55.589 --> 00:57.258
AND THE LORD SAID,

00:57.291 --> 01:01.129
EVERYONE WHO LIVES IN SIN
IS A SLAVE TO SIN.

01:01.162 --> 01:03.664
WHOA TO THE YOUNG LADY WHO
ENFLAMES HERSELF WITH ALCOHOL,

01:03.697 --> 01:08.736
FOR IT POISONS THE BLOOD.

01:08.769 --> 01:12.206
WHAT--WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

01:12.240 --> 01:14.375
SISTER, SISTER, SISTER.

01:14.408 --> 01:16.877
SISTER, SISTER.
SHH.

01:16.910 --> 01:19.147
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

01:19.180 --> 01:20.181
OHH.

01:20.214 --> 01:23.384
- HE RAPED ME.

01:23.417 --> 01:24.718
AGAIN.

01:24.752 --> 01:26.720
- AGAIN?
SHE MENTION THE GUY'S NAME?

01:26.754 --> 01:27.855
- SAYS SHE DOESN'T KNOW IT.

01:27.888 --> 01:30.158
- AND HE ATTACKED HER
HOW MANY TIMES?

01:30.191 --> 01:32.793
- SHE TOLD THE EMTs FOUR
OVER THE PAST 15 YEARS.

01:32.826 --> 01:35.829
- THAT'S A FIRST
FOR A STRANGER RAPIST.

01:35.863 --> 01:36.830
WHAT'S THE VICTIM'S NAME?

01:36.864 --> 01:37.931
- JULIE MCMANUS.

01:37.965 --> 01:40.634
CAME IN DISORIENTED WITH
NUMEROUS SCALP LACERATIONS.

01:40.668 --> 01:43.537
I REMOVED A DOZEN
GLASS SHARDS FROM HER HEAD.

01:43.571 --> 01:46.274
NOW, LOOK, I'M NOT SURE
HOW REAL THIS IS.

01:46.307 --> 01:47.341
- YOU DON'T BELIEVE HER?

01:47.375 --> 01:48.776
- SHE REEKS LIKE A WINO.

01:48.809 --> 01:51.245
I'M WAITING FOR THE RESULTS
ON HER BLOOD ALCOHOL.

01:51.279 --> 01:52.913
- IF SHE SAID THAT
SHE WAS RAPED, SHE WAS RAPED.

01:52.946 --> 01:53.881
- I WASN'T RAPED!

01:53.914 --> 01:56.850
- JULIE, WAIT!

01:56.884 --> 01:57.685
- YOU CALLED THE POLICE?

01:57.718 --> 01:59.753
- JULIE, WE'RE JUST HERE
TO HELP YOU.

01:59.787 --> 02:02.623
- YOU TOLD THE EMTs
THAT YOU WERE RAPED.

02:02.656 --> 02:04.758
DR. TANAKA TOOK
SHARDS OF GLASS

02:04.792 --> 02:05.926
OUT OF YOUR SCALP.

02:05.959 --> 02:07.695
- I'M FINE.
I FELL.

02:07.728 --> 02:08.829
IT'S A MISTAKE.

02:08.862 --> 02:10.298
- JULIE, YOU NEED A RAPE KIT.

02:10.331 --> 02:11.499
THERE COULD
BE EVIDENCE ON YOU

02:11.532 --> 02:12.633
THAT COULD HELP US
FIND THE GUY--

02:12.666 --> 02:14.702
- I JUST HAVE TO GET HOME.

02:14.735 --> 02:15.903
- JULIE!

02:15.936 --> 02:19.873
HEY, DON'T TAKE A SHOWER,
IN CASE YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND.

03:14.928 --> 03:16.364
- PASSENGER THAT GOT ON
THE BUS WITH JULIE

03:16.397 --> 03:18.332
SAW HER STAGGER
OUT OF THIS ALLEY.

03:18.366 --> 03:19.199
- YEAH, BLOOD DROPS.

03:19.233 --> 03:21.335
LEADING FROM THE ALLEY
TO THE BUS STOP.

03:21.369 --> 03:22.703
- HOW FRESH?

03:22.736 --> 03:24.805
- FRESH ENOUGH FOR CSU
TO GET A TYPE A-NEGATIVE.

03:24.838 --> 03:26.240
- OH, SAME AS JULIE'S.

03:26.274 --> 03:28.609
PERP MUST HAVE
ATTACKED HER RIGHT THERE.

03:28.642 --> 03:29.977
- MORE BLOOD
AND BROKEN GLASS.

03:30.010 --> 03:31.712
ANYBODY CATCH WIND?

03:31.745 --> 03:33.347
- ONLY FROM
THE AIR CONDITIONERS.

03:33.381 --> 03:35.649
THE GUY SAID HE HEARD SOME CATS
FIGHTING LATE LAST NIGHT,

03:35.683 --> 03:36.750
BUT HE DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING.

03:36.784 --> 03:37.885
- I FOUND SOMETHIN'!

03:37.918 --> 03:39.453
HEY, CHARLIE,
GET A SHOT OF THIS.

03:39.487 --> 03:40.554
- LAST NIGHT'S GARBAGE?

03:40.588 --> 03:44.292
- NAH, SOMETHING
MUCH MORE VALUABLE.

03:44.325 --> 03:45.693
BROKEN BOTTLE OF BOOZE.

03:45.726 --> 03:46.960
- SAME COLOR
AS THE GLASS SHARDS

03:46.994 --> 03:48.529
FOUND IN JULIE'S SCALP.

03:48.562 --> 03:49.630
- THE BOTTLE'S BUSTED,

03:49.663 --> 03:51.832
LIKE THE PERP GRABBED IT
BY THE NECK AND CROWNED HER.

03:51.865 --> 03:53.734
- OR SHE AND ANOTHER DRUNK
WERE FIGHTING OVER IT,

03:53.767 --> 03:54.968
AND JULIE LOST.

03:55.002 --> 03:56.837
- SHE WASN'T DRUNK.

03:56.870 --> 03:59.873
DOC SAID HE DIDN'T FIND A DROP
OF ALCOHOL IN JULIE'S BLOOD.

03:59.907 --> 04:01.642
- HER NAME IS NOT JULIE MCMANUS.

04:01.675 --> 04:04.478
CSU GOT A HIT OFF
A THUMBPRINT FROM THE BOTTLE.

04:04.512 --> 04:08.516
AND IT BELONGS TO A WOMAN
NAMED VICKI ALICIA SAYERS.

04:08.549 --> 04:10.050
- WELL, SHE GAVE
THE HOSPITAL A FAKE NAME.

04:10.083 --> 04:10.851
HAS SHE BEEN
IN ANY TROUBLE?

04:10.884 --> 04:11.819
- NO, HER PRINTS
ARE IN THE SYSTEM

04:11.852 --> 04:14.054
BECAUSE SHE APPLIED
FOR A CIVIL SERVANT JOB.

04:14.087 --> 04:15.589
- ADDRESS IS IN MID-TOWN.

04:15.623 --> 04:17.325
- YEAH, THAT'S BOGUS.
THERE'S NO PHONE.

04:17.358 --> 04:20.060
THERE'S NO RECORD OF
A VICKI SAYERS IN THE TRISTATE.

04:20.093 --> 04:21.929
TRYING TO MAKE HERSELF
INVISIBLE.

04:21.962 --> 04:23.364
- I DON'T BLAME HER.

04:23.397 --> 04:24.598
SHE'S BEEN RAPED FOUR TIMES
BY THE SAME GUY.

04:24.632 --> 04:25.899
- OLIVIA...

04:25.933 --> 04:27.301
- OH, I KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE GONNA SAY, CAPTAIN.

04:27.335 --> 04:29.670
- NO COMPLAINING WITNESS,
NO CASE.

04:29.703 --> 04:32.039
- I WAS GOING TO SAY
IF THERE'S A RAPIST OUT THERE,

04:32.072 --> 04:34.708
WE'LL DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO COLLAR HIM.

04:34.742 --> 04:37.311
- WELL, THE ODDS ARE THAT SHE
LIVES OR WORKS

04:37.345 --> 04:38.546
NEAR THE AREA
SHE WAS ATTACKED.

04:38.579 --> 04:39.713
- YEAH, BUT WE CAN'T BE
KNOCKING ON EVERY DOOR

04:39.747 --> 04:41.048
IN THE WASHINGTON HEIGHTS
AREA.

04:41.081 --> 04:43.851
- BUT WE CAN CHECK HER OUT
THROUGH THE TAX MAN.

04:43.884 --> 04:46.987
SHE'D HAVE TO USE HER REAL NAME
TO PAY THE PIPER.

04:47.020 --> 04:49.390
GET A SUBPOENA
FOR THE CITY TAX ROLLS.

04:52.593 --> 04:55.329
[doorbell buzzing]

04:57.531 --> 04:58.666
- VICKI.

04:58.699 --> 05:00.701
VICKI SAYERS,
I'M DETECTIVE BENSON.

05:00.734 --> 05:03.371
WE MET AT THE HOSPITAL
LAST NIGHT.

05:03.404 --> 05:05.339
[doorbell buzzing]

05:08.542 --> 05:09.510
- HEY.

05:09.543 --> 05:11.011
- VICKI!

05:11.044 --> 05:12.846
VICKI, LISTEN TO ME.

05:12.880 --> 05:14.515
I UNDERSTAND
WHY YOU'RE SCARED,

05:14.548 --> 05:15.883
BUT WE'RE HERE
TO PROTECT YOU.

05:15.916 --> 05:18.686
I JUST--I JUST NEED YOU
TO TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED,

05:18.719 --> 05:20.888
SO I CAN STOP HIM.

05:23.924 --> 05:25.359
- HOW DID YOU FIND ME?

05:25.393 --> 05:27.695
- YOU PAID YOUR TAXES.
- OH, GOD.

05:27.728 --> 05:29.930
- VICKI, PLEASE LET ME IN!
I CAN HELP YOU.

05:29.963 --> 05:31.098
- NO, YOU CAN'T.

05:31.131 --> 05:33.434
NO ONE CAN.
GO AWAY!

05:33.467 --> 05:34.468
- HOLD ON.
VICKI!

05:34.502 --> 05:35.503
[knocks on window]

05:35.536 --> 05:37.671
VICKI!

05:42.410 --> 05:45.513
- I KNOW, I KNOW.
WE'RE GONNA BE HERE FOR A WHILE.

05:47.748 --> 05:48.982
- HEADS UP.

05:49.016 --> 05:52.052
WE GOT A FEMALE DELIVERING BAGS
TO VICKI'S DOOR.

05:52.085 --> 05:55.523
- CAN YOU SEE WHAT'S IN THEM?

05:55.556 --> 05:56.957
- YEAH, LOOKS LIKE GROCERIES
IN ONE,

05:56.990 --> 05:58.392
AND OFFICE SUPPLIES
IN THE OTHER.

05:58.426 --> 06:01.061
- VICKI COMING OUT
TO GET 'EM?

06:01.094 --> 06:05.065
- NO, OUR DELIVERY LADY
KNOWS THE OUTSIDE DOOR CODE.

06:07.801 --> 06:10.170
VICKI'S SO PARANOID,
SHE DOESN'T LEAVE THE HOUSE.

06:10.203 --> 06:11.872
SHE PROBABLY
HAS A THROWAWAY CELL TOO.

06:11.905 --> 06:13.441
- SO WE CAN'T TRACE IT.

06:13.474 --> 06:17.411
RULE NUMBER ONE IN
THE STALKING VICTIMS' HANDBOOK.

06:17.445 --> 06:19.980
LET'S SEE IF SHE KNOWS
WHEN VICKI'S COMING OUT.

06:24.217 --> 06:26.887
- EXCUSE ME.

06:26.920 --> 06:29.423
POLICE.

06:29.457 --> 06:31.091
- ME?
- YEAH.

06:31.124 --> 06:34.728
HOW LONG YOU BEEN WORKING
FOR VICKI SAYERS?

06:34.762 --> 06:36.730
- I COULD LOSE MY JOB
IF I SAY ANYTHING.

06:36.764 --> 06:40.768
- WELL, SHE COULD
LOSE HER LIFE IF YOU DON'T.

06:40.801 --> 06:42.536
- I RUN ALL HER ERRANDS

06:42.570 --> 06:44.104
SO SHE DOESN'T
HAVE TO LEAVE THE HOUSE.

06:44.137 --> 06:46.039
I PAY HER BILLS
SO HER MONEY CAN'T BE TRACED.

06:46.073 --> 06:47.741
- DOES SHE HAVE A JOB?

06:47.775 --> 06:49.076
- UH...

06:49.109 --> 06:50.110
MEDICAL ACCOUNTING.

06:50.143 --> 06:50.978
SHE WORKS FROM HOME.

06:51.011 --> 06:52.813
ONLY GOES INTO AN OFFICE
ONCE A MONTH.

06:52.846 --> 06:55.883
- WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME?
- YESTERDAY.

06:55.916 --> 06:57.885
THAT'S ALL I CAN TELL YOU.
I HAVE TO GO.

07:10.197 --> 07:14.067
- VICKI.
VICKI, I GET IT.

07:14.101 --> 07:14.935
YOU KNOW THAT HE'S
WATCHING YOU

07:14.968 --> 07:16.937
BECAUSE HE ATTACKED YOU
ON THE ONE DAY

07:16.970 --> 07:18.171
THAT YOU LEFT YOUR HOUSE.

07:18.205 --> 07:22.476
AND YOU KNOW
THAT HE'S COMING BACK.

07:22.510 --> 07:23.711
VICKI.

07:23.744 --> 07:24.978
PLEASE LET ME IN.

07:25.012 --> 07:26.647
I CAN HELP YOU.

07:36.524 --> 07:38.859
- SO IS SHE
LOOKING AT US AGAIN?

07:38.892 --> 07:40.794
- WELL, MAYBE IF SHE SEES
WE'RE SERIOUS,

07:40.828 --> 07:42.062
SHE'LL COME OUT.

07:42.095 --> 07:43.531
- MAYBE WE SHOULD
SMOKE HER OUT.

07:43.564 --> 07:45.198
- LOOK, JUST GIVE ME
A COUPLE MORE HOURS, OKAY?

07:45.232 --> 07:47.568
I, UH, MAYBE SHE'LL
CHANGE HER MIND.

07:47.601 --> 07:49.937
- I GOTTA GET BACK TO THE SQUAD,
PREP FOR COURT.

07:49.970 --> 07:51.171
- AH, OKAY.

07:51.204 --> 07:53.140
WELL, YOU TAKE THE CAR,
AND GO.

07:53.173 --> 07:54.675
I'LL HANG.

07:54.708 --> 07:55.743
[car starts]

07:55.776 --> 07:58.712
I'LL CALL FIN,
HAVE HIM SPELL ME.

07:58.746 --> 07:59.780
- SEE YA.

08:26.306 --> 08:28.241
SVU PORTABLE ONE TO TWO.

08:28.275 --> 08:29.877
FIN, HOW FAR OUT ARE YOU?

08:29.910 --> 08:31.979
- I GOT HUNG UP BY THE SQUAD.
YOU OKAY?

08:32.012 --> 08:33.547
- OKAY, UH, VICKI'S ON THE MOVE.

08:33.581 --> 08:36.049
I'M JUST GONNA
HAVE TO IMPROVISE.

08:36.083 --> 08:38.619
HEY...POLICE!

08:42.189 --> 08:43.023
FOLLOW THAT CAR.

08:43.056 --> 08:46.594
DO AS I SAY.
GO, GO.

09:25.198 --> 09:26.299
[gasps]
- VICKI, STOP!

09:26.333 --> 09:28.702
VICKI! VICKI, STOP!

09:28.736 --> 09:30.037
- OH! [gasps]

09:30.070 --> 09:32.105
- VICKI, VICKI, VICKI.
LISTEN, IT'S ME, OLIVIA!

09:32.139 --> 09:34.574
- [whimpering and panting]

09:37.177 --> 09:38.345
LEAVE ME ALONE.

09:38.378 --> 09:39.947
- VICKI, DROP THE GUN.

09:39.980 --> 09:42.616
- NO, I--
I HAVE TO PROTECT MYSELF.

09:42.650 --> 09:44.151
- I'M GONNA PROTECT YOU, VICKI.

09:44.184 --> 09:45.653
I PROMISE.

09:45.686 --> 09:47.755
NOW DROP THE GUN. NOW.

09:49.690 --> 09:51.058
NOW!

09:57.931 --> 09:59.900
- I'M SORRY.

09:59.933 --> 10:02.135
I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

10:02.169 --> 10:05.806
- YOU'RE UNDER ARREST FOR
CRIMINAL POSSESSION OF A WEAPON.

10:05.839 --> 10:07.841
- PLEASE DON'T DO THIS TO ME.
[handcuffs snapping]

10:07.875 --> 10:08.909
PLEASE.

10:14.748 --> 10:16.249
- I'M THE ONE WHO WAS RAPED,
AND YOU'RE ARRESTING ME?

10:16.283 --> 10:17.284
- YOU'RE LUCKY
I DIDN'T SHOOT YOU

10:17.317 --> 10:19.787
WITH THAT GUN IN YOUR HAND.

10:19.820 --> 10:22.022
- HOW ELSE AM I SUPPOSED
TO PROTECT MYSELF?

10:22.055 --> 10:26.860
- BY HELPING ME CATCH THE GUY
WHO'S BEEN ATTACKING YOU.

10:26.894 --> 10:29.229
- HE'S TOO SMART.
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA GET HIM.

10:29.262 --> 10:30.964
- I WILL, IF YOU'D TRUST ME.

10:30.998 --> 10:32.065
- TRUST YOU?

10:32.099 --> 10:34.201
YOU'RE STALKING ME,
JUST LIKE HE IS.

10:34.234 --> 10:35.368
- HAVING A GUN DELIVERED

10:35.402 --> 10:37.671
LIKE IT'S SOME KIND
OF CHINESE TAKE-OUT?

10:37.705 --> 10:38.672
THAT'S THE ANSWER?

10:38.706 --> 10:41.341
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT ELSE TO DO.

10:47.047 --> 10:51.384
- I'M SORRY, VICKI.
I PUSHED YOU.

10:51.418 --> 10:54.021
I JUST DON'T KNOW
IF WE HAVE ANY TIME LEFT.

10:54.054 --> 10:55.889
- WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

10:55.923 --> 10:57.457
- HE'S ESCALATING.

10:57.490 --> 11:00.894
HE NEARLY KILLED YOU
WITH THAT BOTTLE.

11:00.928 --> 11:03.897
NEXT TIME, HE WILL.

11:08.135 --> 11:10.003
- I'M SCARED.

11:10.037 --> 11:13.907
- THAT'S WHY I NEED YOU
TO TALK TO ME.

11:22.049 --> 11:23.917
YOU HAVEN'T
CHANGED YOUR CLOTHES.

11:23.951 --> 11:29.222
AND I CAN SEE...
THAT YOU DIDN'T SHOWER.

11:29.256 --> 11:31.391
- YOU SAID I SHOULDN'T.

11:31.424 --> 11:33.260
- I KNOW YOU WANT TO CATCH
THIS SON OF A BITCH

11:33.293 --> 11:34.461
AS MUCH AS I DO.

11:34.494 --> 11:37.297
SO COME, I'M GONNA TAKE YOU
TO THE HOSPITAL, ALL RIGHT?

11:37.330 --> 11:38.498
- IT'S NOT TOO LATE?

11:38.531 --> 11:43.003
- WE CAN RECOVER EVIDENCE
UP TO 96 HOURS AFTER THE ATTACK.

11:48.842 --> 11:50.510
- WILL YOU STAY WITH ME?

11:50.543 --> 11:54.047
- FOR AS LONG AS IT TAKES.

11:54.081 --> 11:58.485
- FIRST TIME HE RAPED ME
WAS 1995.

11:58.518 --> 12:01.221
I WAS 16.

12:01.254 --> 12:04.157
I WAS A CANDY STRIPER
AT A HOSPITAL.

12:09.362 --> 12:14.034
WHEN I WAS LEAVING...

12:14.067 --> 12:15.335
HE GRABBED ME FROM BEHIND.

12:15.368 --> 12:16.736
HE HAD A KNIFE.

12:18.571 --> 12:21.775
AND HE PUSHED ME
INTO A STOREROOM CLOSET.

12:21.809 --> 12:24.444
PULLED UP MY DRESS AND...

12:24.477 --> 12:29.382
AND HE LOOKED ME IN THE EYES
WHILE HE RAPED ME.

12:29.416 --> 12:31.318
- AND YOU DIDN'T KNOW HIM?

12:31.351 --> 12:34.487
- NO, I HAD NEVER
SEEN HIM BEFORE.

12:34.521 --> 12:36.056
- DID HE SAY ANYTHING?

12:36.089 --> 12:39.492
- HE SAID, "YOU BETTER
BE A GOOD GIRL.

12:39.526 --> 12:41.761
AND BEHAVE."

12:44.264 --> 12:46.533
HE TOLD ME THAT HE WOULD
KILL MY MOM AND DAD

12:46.566 --> 12:50.203
IF I TOLD ANYONE.

12:52.305 --> 12:54.374
AND THEN HE TOOK
MY DRIVER'S PERMIT

12:54.407 --> 12:57.210
SO THAT HE WOULD KNOW MY NAME
AND WHERE I LIVED.

12:57.244 --> 13:00.080
- WHEN WAS THE NEXT ATTACK?

13:00.113 --> 13:03.383
- NOVEMBER 14, 1998.

13:03.416 --> 13:06.453
I WAS A SOPHOMORE AT HUDSON.

13:06.486 --> 13:09.422
HE HELD A KNIFE TO MY THROAT,
AND HE SAID,

13:09.456 --> 13:10.924
"I'VE BEEN LOOKING
ALL OVER FOR YOU.

13:10.958 --> 13:13.393
YOU'VE BEEN A VERY BAD GIRL."

13:13.426 --> 13:14.928
- HE BROKE INTO YOUR APARTMENT?

13:14.962 --> 13:16.429
- FROM THE FIRE ESCAPE.

13:16.463 --> 13:19.499
[camera clicking]

13:19.532 --> 13:20.433
[voice cracking]
HE TIED ME UP

13:20.467 --> 13:22.102
AND THEN HE TOLD ME
TO GET ON MY KNEES.

13:22.135 --> 13:23.470
[sniffles]

13:23.503 --> 13:25.405
- IT'S OKAY, VICKI.

13:25.438 --> 13:27.474
IT'S OKAY, TAKE YOUR TIME.

13:27.507 --> 13:30.911
- HE RAPED ME
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

13:30.944 --> 13:33.080
THE WHOLE TIME, HE JUST
KEPT WHISPERING,

13:33.113 --> 13:34.982
"YOU'RE MINE.

13:35.015 --> 13:37.450
FOREVER."

13:37.484 --> 13:39.452
[sobbing]

13:42.455 --> 13:43.556
- DID YOU CALL THE POLICE?

13:43.590 --> 13:45.392
- YES.

13:45.425 --> 13:46.493
THEY DID A REPORT,

13:46.526 --> 13:48.161
BUT I DIDN'T
GO TO THE HOSPITAL.

13:48.195 --> 13:51.498
I JUST WANTED TO FORGET
IT HAD EVER HAPPENED.

13:51.531 --> 13:54.434
UNTIL MY 20TH BIRTHDAY.

13:54.467 --> 13:58.171
I GOT HOME, AND THERE WAS
A PACKAGE WAITING FOR ME.

13:58.205 --> 14:00.540
WHEN I OPENED IT, THERE WAS
A JACK-IN-THE-BOX INSIDE

14:00.573 --> 14:03.210
THAT SANG HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

14:03.243 --> 14:05.946
AND THE CARD ATTACHED SAID,
"I'M WATCHING YOU.

14:05.979 --> 14:07.915
BEHAVE YOURSELF."

14:09.482 --> 14:11.051
- HE KNEW
IT WAS YOUR BIRTHDAY

14:11.084 --> 14:12.285
BECAUSE HE HAD
YOUR DRIVING PERMIT.

14:12.319 --> 14:16.156
- I WAS TOO SCARED
TO TELL THE POLICE.

14:16.189 --> 14:18.425
