WHETHER EVIDENCE

38:03.615 --> 38:05.751
OF AN UNCHARGED CRIME
FROM ANOTHER STATE

38:05.784 --> 38:08.086
CAN BE USED HERE

38:08.119 --> 38:12.758
TO IDENTIFY THE DEFENDANT
AS MS. SAYERS' RAPIST.

38:12.791 --> 38:15.327
IT IS A TRAVESTY
THAT THE EVIDENCE

38:15.361 --> 38:18.564
WHICH COULD PROVE WILLIAM HARRIS
RAPED VICKI SAYERS

38:18.597 --> 38:22.033
SAT UNTESTED
FOR MORE THAN A DECADE.

38:22.067 --> 38:24.035
UNFORTUNATELY,
THIS HAPPENS EVERY DAY.

38:24.069 --> 38:25.671
ALL OVER THE COUNTRY.

38:25.704 --> 38:28.640
BUT ONCE THE EVIDENCE
WAS FINALLY TESTED,

38:28.674 --> 38:30.909
TOO MUCH TIME HAD PASSED.

38:30.942 --> 38:34.946
SO THE DNA HAD BECOME
SIGNIFICANTLY DEGRADED.

38:34.980 --> 38:37.115
AND BECAUSE THE SAMPLE WAS
STORED IN CALIFORNIA,

38:37.148 --> 38:38.717
THE PEOPLE CAN'T PROVE

38:38.750 --> 38:41.420
THE CHAIN OF CUSTODY
WAS PRESERVED.

38:41.453 --> 38:44.490
THEREFORE I HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT TO RULE THE DNA

38:44.523 --> 38:47.626
INSUFFICIENT TO CORROBORATE
MS. SAYERS IDENTIFICATION

38:47.659 --> 38:50.796
OF MR. HARRIS.

38:50.829 --> 38:53.064
I AM VERY SORRY,
BUT I HAVE NO CHOICE.

38:53.098 --> 38:56.001
THIS CASE IS DISMISSED
WITHOUT PREJUDICE.

38:56.034 --> 39:00.406
THE PEOPLE CAN REFILE CHARGES
IF NEW EVIDENCE IS UNCOVERED.

39:00.439 --> 39:02.574
WE ARE ADJOURNED.

39:02.608 --> 39:03.742
- HOW CAN SHE DO THAT?

39:03.775 --> 39:05.043
- WE'LL GET HIM, VICKI.
I PROMISE.

39:05.076 --> 39:08.980
- JUST STOP MAKING PROMISES
THAT YOU CAN'T KEEP.

39:09.014 --> 39:10.716
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA GET HIM.

39:10.749 --> 39:13.084
I WAS STUPID TO THINK THAT
THERE'D EVER BE ANY JUSTICE.

39:13.118 --> 39:14.620
- VICKI...

39:17.088 --> 39:19.658
[door slams]

39:19.691 --> 39:21.126
[sighs]

39:25.497 --> 39:28.467
- THE FBI's TAKEN OVER
HARRIS'S CASE.

39:28.500 --> 39:30.469
I ALREADY GAVE THEM ALL
THE VICTIMS' DRIVER'S LICENSES.

39:30.502 --> 39:32.738
THEY'LL BE COMING BACK LATER
FOR THE REST.

39:32.771 --> 39:34.940
- I WONDER HOW MANY GUYS LIKE
HARRIS COULD HAVE BEEN STOPPED

39:34.973 --> 39:37.008
IF THOSE RAPE KITS
HAD BEEN TESTED.

39:37.042 --> 39:39.711
- WELL, UNTIL THEY ARE,

39:39.745 --> 39:42.047
EVERYONE IS JUST A VICTIM
WHO'S NEVER GONNA SEE JUSTICE.

39:42.080 --> 39:44.450
- IT'S LIKE WE'RE TELLING THEM
THAT THEY DON'T MATTER

39:44.483 --> 39:48.754
AND WE'RE TELLING THE PERPS
THAT THEY CAN GET AWAY WITH IT.

39:53.124 --> 39:54.626
OH, MY GOD.

39:54.660 --> 39:56.027
- WHAT?

39:56.061 --> 39:58.163
- WE MAY HAVE HAD HIM
ALL ALONG.

40:08.039 --> 40:09.975
- VICKI!

40:10.008 --> 40:11.777
VICKI! OPEN THE DOOR!
[ringing buzzer]

40:11.810 --> 40:13.812
IT'S DETECTIVE BENSON.
IT'S IMPORTANT.

40:15.847 --> 40:17.549
- WHAT DO YOU WANT NOW?

40:17.583 --> 40:18.950
- I NEED TO ASK YOU...

40:18.984 --> 40:21.620
ABOUT WHEN HARRIS ATTACKED YOU
IN 1998.

40:21.653 --> 40:24.122
- WHY WOULD YOU WANT ME
TO GO THROUGH THAT AGAIN?

40:24.155 --> 40:27.826
- HOW LONG DID HE STAY?

40:27.859 --> 40:28.827
- WHY?

40:28.860 --> 40:30.729
- JUST TELL ME.

40:30.762 --> 40:34.566
HOW LONG DID HARRIS STAY?

40:34.600 --> 40:36.201
- ALL NIGHT
AND INTO THE NEXT DAY.

40:36.234 --> 40:37.703
- DID HE FORCE YOU
AGAINST YOUR WILL?

40:37.736 --> 40:39.971
- I ALREADY TOLD YOU,
HE TIED ME UP.

40:40.005 --> 40:41.973
- WITH WHAT?

40:42.007 --> 40:45.477
WHAT DID HE TIE YOU UP WITH?

40:45.511 --> 40:47.245
- DUCT TAPE.

40:47.278 --> 40:50.081
HE DIDN'T EVEN TAKE IT OFF...
BEFORE HE LEFT.

40:50.115 --> 40:51.850
IT TOOK HOURS FOR ME
TO BREAK FREE

40:51.883 --> 40:53.752
AND CALL THE POLICE.

40:53.785 --> 40:56.121
- VICKI, DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED TO THAT DUCT TAPE?

40:56.154 --> 40:58.023
- YES.

40:58.056 --> 41:01.126
YES, THE POLICE OFFICERS,
THEY PUT IT IN A BAG.

41:01.159 --> 41:02.628
THEY SAID THAT THEY
WERE GONNA KEEP IT

41:02.661 --> 41:04.930
IN CASE THE DETECTIVES
EVER FOUND A SUSPECT.

41:04.963 --> 41:06.665
BUT NOBODY EVER CALLED ME.

41:06.698 --> 41:10.769
- BECAUSE...YOUR
POLICE REPORT GOT LOST.

41:10.802 --> 41:12.037
WE NEVER KNEW IT WAS THERE.

41:15.607 --> 41:17.843
- I HAVE TO GO TO SEATTLE
AND PORTLAND NEXT WEEK,

41:17.876 --> 41:20.111
BUT I'LL BE BACK
FRIDAY NIGHT.

41:20.145 --> 41:21.547
WHEN CAN I SEE YOU AGAIN?

41:21.580 --> 41:23.982
[handcuff snaps]
- IN ABOUT 25 YEARS.

41:24.015 --> 41:25.951
- I HAVEN'T GONE NEAR
THAT WOMAN!

41:25.984 --> 41:28.153
- WILLIAM HARRIS,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

41:28.186 --> 41:30.856
- WHAT THE HELL FOR THIS TIME?

41:30.889 --> 41:32.257
- KIDNAPPING
IN THE FIRST DEGREE.

41:32.290 --> 41:34.125
- I DIDN'T KIDNAP HER.

41:34.159 --> 41:35.226
- YEAH, YOU DID.
WHEN YOU RAPED HER IN '98.

41:35.260 --> 41:36.828
- YOU HELD HER HOSTAGE
IN HER APARTMENT

41:36.862 --> 41:38.129
FOR MORE THAN 12 HOURS.

41:38.163 --> 41:40.599
AND WE HAVE THE DUCT TAPE
TO PROVE IT.

41:42.167 --> 41:44.536
- YOU CAN'T DO THIS!
- WELL, YEAH, WE CAN.

41:44.570 --> 41:46.672
AND WE ARE.

41:46.705 --> 41:49.107
SEE, THERE'S NO STATUTE
OF LIMITATIONS ON KIDNAPPING.

41:49.140 --> 41:51.109
- VICKI, PLEASE TELL THEM
THEY'RE WRONG.

41:51.142 --> 41:52.944
YOU KNOW IT WASN'T RAPE.
I LOVE YOU.

41:52.978 --> 41:55.747
I LO--UH, I LOVE YOU!

41:59.651 --> 42:02.654
- NOW I'LL ALWAYS KNOW
WHERE YOU ARE.

